## **Helpful Commands Reference**

### **NPM Workflow (Recommended)**
```bash
# Start services
npm start                    # Smart starter (see ./scripts/start.sh --help)
npm run dev                  # Base + dev overlay
npm run dev:full             # base + dev + email + S3

# Testing and monitoring
npm run health               # Service health
npm test                     # Full test suite (health + auth + db)
npm run test:auth            # Authentication

# Utilities
npm run logs                 # All service logs
npm stop                     # docker compose down
npm run reset                # Interactive reset (preserves Ollama models)
./scripts/reset.sh --clear-ollama  # Reset including Ollama volumes
```

### **Direct Docker Commands (Alternative)**
```bash
# Container management
docker compose ps                    # View running services
docker compose restart [service]    # Restart specific service
docker compose down && docker compose up -d  # Full restart

# Database access
docker exec -it supabase-db psql -U postgres

# Reset with options
./scripts/reset.sh                   # Standard reset (preserve Ollama)
./scripts/reset.sh --clear-ollama    # Remove everything including Ollama models
./scripts/reset.sh --dev-email       # Include email server cleanup
```

